# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your subscription token.
#
# The "Fix" button uses the Claude Code headless CLI (`claude -p`) with your
# Claude Max/Pro subscription — NOT an API key.
#
# 1. Install Claude Code:            https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/claude-code
# 2. Generate a long-lived token:    claude setup-token
#    (opens a browser, authenticates against your Max/Pro subscription,
#     then prints a token starting with "sk-ant-oat...")
# 3. Paste that token below, save this file as ".env" (no quotes needed).
#
# .env is git-ignored — never commit your token.

CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oat-your-token-here
